    • Constructor Detail

      • Station

        public Station​(java.lang.String name,
               double latitude,
               double longitude)
        Constructor for the Station object. Accepts the name, latitude and longitude information and initialises these class variable fields. Other fields are initialised from another method in the utils.LatestWeather class.
        Parameters:
        name - Station Name from user input or read from file.
        latitude - GPS Latitude co-ordinates in Decimal Decrees, from user input or read from file.
        longitude - GPS Longitude co-ordinates in Decimal Decrees from user input or read from file.
